{
  "texts": [
    "15 LLMs possess a range of capabilities which may be applied to the clinical domain, one of which is text summarization.",
    "Previous reports have evaluated the potential use of LLMs in summarizing scientific literature, radiology reports, patient problem lists and doctor-patient conversations, with varying success.",
    "16, 17 However, there has been limited research on the ability of LLMs to summarize information from a patient's hospital encounter into a discharge summary.",
    "18 As ambient AI scribes and other LLM-based tools begin to be deployed within healthcare settings, 19 rigorous evaluations of the accuracy of these technologies are urgently needed.",
    "In this study, we investigate the performance of two state-of-the-art LLMs, GPT-4 and GPT-3.5turbo, in generating ED discharge summaries and evaluate the prevalence and type of errors across each section of the discharge summary."
  ]
}